      "title": "TTDN1 Interactors Identification Analysis",
      "additionalAttributes": [],
      "projectDescription": "TTDN1 interactors were identified from HeLa-S cells.",
      "sampleProcessingProtocol": "Transduced HeLa-S cells were used for stable expression of Flag-tagged TTDN1. Nuclear extract was prepared from the stable cell lines and the TTDN1 complexes were purified using anti-Flag resin (M2; Sigma) in TAP buffer (50 mM Tris-HCl pH 7.9, 100 mM KCl, 5 mM MgCl2, 10% glycerol, 0.1% NP-40, 1 mM DTT, and protease inhibitors). After elution in TAP buffer plus 0.4 mg/mL Flag peptide, the complexes were TCA precipitated.",
